                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The nuclear mummy's touch carries a mutating radiation. An infected creature can't heal damage it takes from unholy radiation until it has been cured of the disease</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:20]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Damage[1d6[poison]] damage (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Damage[1d6[poison]] damage (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @Damage[1d6[poison]] damage (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead, rising as a nuclear zombie (using a driftdead returned's statistics)</p>"
